My hook file in this place.
.git/hooks/post-commit

My hook file do:
Print GIT_AUTHOR_NAME and GIT_AUTHOR_DATE and displays the full path from the root directory to the current working directory.

To learn hook I enjoyed from this site.
https://www.digitalocean.com/community/tutorials/how-to-use-git-hooks-to-automate-development-and-deployment-tasks?fbclid=IwAR2V955jqazk38hJ88d0ShASt1gA-Z8IZ7CvjfIEQIQkY65B4quOWyfH3P0#setting-up-a-repository
